title: Episode 18 - The Markets Hit A 52-week High... So Why Am I Losing Money?
itunes:title: The Markets Hit A 52-week High... So Why Am I Losing Money?
description: Frank breaks down the difficulty of investing in a market where the government chooses winners and losers. Oil expert Matt Badiali from Stansberry & Associates is bullish on oil but bearish on nat gas. Rich Suttmeier from Valuengine.com sees the Dow at 8500.
